fields.name: hillington-car boot organiser
fields.description: this hillington car boot organiser will manage your muddy shoes, boots, magazines, books and your camping or clothing stuff, your travel comes easy with this car traveling gadget with universal size and color. this multi-functional car boot organizer - great for storing and organizing a variety of items.  features four large pockets and three extra-strong adjustable straps with clips. if you spend a lot of time in and out of the car taking the kids to school, driving to work, heading off for days in the country or taking the dog out on a walk, this versatile organizer is right up your street. provides space to store, sort and organize your essential items and keep them neat and orderly until you need them. use it to keep kids’ toys close at hand or tuck away cans of windscreen defroster, air fresheners, jump cables, car cleaning accessories, dog treats and much more! you’ll create bags more space in your boot and be able to lay your hands on anything you need at a moment’s notice. lightweight design fits most vehicle makes and models, can be installed in seconds and can be easily rolled away for storage.

fields.name: gadlane-car organiser
fields.description:
the gadlane universal car boot organiser boasts a number of quality features such as a hook and loop base for secure attachment to the car boot lining to help it stay secure during travel avoiding items spilling into the boot. a universal fitting letting it be used in most car boots providing they have the space (50w x 38cm x 26h size of organiser). compartments in the boot organiser are easily adjustable to the items you have reassuring you that they will stay secure when you’re on the move. side compartments also are attached for smaller items such as hand tools, safety equipment, gloves and other items. if the product gets dirty which it will in some circumstances, the material is easy to clean with minimal hassle.


organise - this gadlane boot storage organiser has several compartments which can be adjusted to the requirements; depending on the amount and size of the items.
dimensions - 50w x 38cm x 26h in size which will fit most car boots and has a universal fitting with a hook and loop base for secure attachment to the boot carpet lining ensuring that items will not move or spill when on the move.
easy clean - easy to clean material ensures minimal effort and hassle free wash. folds away quickly and neatly when not in use and for easy storage.
compartments - this car boot tidy also has side pockets and compartments for smaller items such as hand tools, gloves, torches etc.
versatile - for all items such as safety equipment, car cleaning products, building & garage tools along with groceries etc.
